}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Our Hospital</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">
        Welcome to our hospital, where we prioritize your health and well-being.
        Our team of experienced doctors, nurses, and staff are committed to providing
        compassionate and top-quality care.
    </p>
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
                To deliver exceptional healthcare services with a focus on patient satisfaction,
