            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>
                To become a globally recognized hospital, known for outstanding care and state-of-the-art facilities.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</div>

